		<div id="maintext" class="odd">
			<p><h1 class="about">ABOUT THE FESTIVAL</h1>
Punchbowl Farm Festival began in a Wiltshire country garden in 2009; a festival to round off the summer with beautiful sounds, playtime with new and old friends and, most importantly, to raise money for an incredible local charity.<br/>
… peacocks, music, sun, joyous, yummy, beautiful, happy, magical …<br/><br/>
Please check out our Facebook page for all the latest news and to see pictures from previous years <br /><a href="http://www.facebook.com/PunchbowlFestival">Facebook</a><br />
‘A friendly family festival in a beautiful location; lovely laid-back atmosphere, great music, great food, good times!’ Rosie, Wiltshire<br/><br/>
‘Something for all the family, and late night owls!’ Francesca, Bristol<br/><br/>
<br/> </p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div id="imagebox">
		<img src="/assets/15/sign_crop.jpg"  alt='punchbowl_sign' />
	</div>
	
